00:03:42.599 --> 00:03:47.270
Now for an exercise we can do to practice.
You will need as many balls as you have, 4

00:03:47.270 --> 00:03:53.109
cones and a lot of space. Please don't do
this in your backyard and break your parent's

00:03:53.109 --> 00:03:53.649
windows!

00:03:53.649 --> 00:04:00.649
Start off by taking a few swings without the
ball. Get your body use to how this will feel.

00:04:05.190 --> 00:04:09.669
Once comfortable get the ball out and take
some swings. Don't worry about accuracy or

00:04:09.669 --> 00:04:15.399
distance yet. Focus on technique. You could
even start with chipping the ball a few times

00:04:15.399 --> 00:04:18.470
and then progress to height and distance.

00:04:18.470 --> 00:04:24.390
When you feel confident with your technique
set up four cones as a square target up the

00:04:24.390 --> 00:04:29.410
field. Try to kick the ball high and far and
make it land in the square.

00:04:29.410 --> 00:04:34.040
Repeat until you master it or feel tired.
Make sure you are good and warmed up and don't

00:04:34.040 --> 00:04:41.040
do this for an hour. I don't want you pulling
anything!

00:04:54.990 --> 00:04:56.450
Some things that could be going wrong.

00:04:56.450 --> 00:05:01.380
If your plant foot is to close to the ball
then you can't get the proper swing. You will

00:05:01.380 --> 00:05:06.640
end up using the inside of your foot, not
rotating your foot down like I talked about

00:05:06.640 --> 00:05:08.570
in Key Point #4.

00:05:08.570 --> 00:05:14.510
If you aren't getting much height check your
backswing. Most players have a high back swing.

00:05:14.510 --> 00:05:17.990
Don't kick your leg out when you step to the
ball. Instead take a step to the ball and

00:05:17.990 --> 00:05:23.160
let your back leg trail behind you.

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:29.520
Increase your kicking leg speed as your technique
improves. Technique equals power. When your

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:35.040
technique is solid then you can add more pure
strength to your swing. Do this by increasing

00:05:35.040 --> 00:05:39.880
the speed at which you swing your kicking
leg to strike the ball. This will equal greater

00:05:39.880 --> 00:05:42.000
distance on your kicks.

